<span id="Actions"></span>
=== Ações ===

No perfil de um usuário, você pode realizar diversas ações, que variam dependendo se você adicionou o usuário como amigo ou não.

[[File:UserProfile_UserActions.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Actions available for a non-friended user.</span>]]
[[File:UserProfile_FriendActions.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Actions available for a friended user.</span>]]


{| class="wikitable"
!<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Action</span>
!<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Description</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Join<ref group="actions" name="friends-only">These actions can only be performed on friends.</ref></span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Joins the user's instance.</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Request Invite<ref group="actions" name="friends-only"></ref></span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Sends the user a notification informing them that you would like to join their instance. The notification includes a customizable message and with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] a photo can also be added to the notification.</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Send Invite<ref group="actions" name="friends-only"></ref></span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Sends the user an invitation to join your instance. The invite includes a customizable message and with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] a photo can also be added to the invitation.</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Gift VRC+</span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Opens a menu that allows you to buy [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] for the user. ''See [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+#Gifting|Gifting]] for more detailed information.''</span>
